}}</ref>2016年與2017年三百多萬美元的收入中，超過90%來自會員捐款。<ref>{{cite web | url=https://www.savetibet.org/wp-content/uploads/2018/09/2017-Audit.pdf | title=International Campaign for Tibet Financial Statements and Supplementary Information For the Years Ended December 31 , 2017 and 2016 | access-date=2019-03-16 | archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20181018115813/http://www.savetibet.org/wp-content/uploads/2018/09/2017-Audit.pdf | archive-date=2018-10-18 | dead-url=yes }}</ref>它有時接受[[美国国家民主基金会|美国国家民主基金会]]一年数万美元的捐款<ref>{{Cite web |url=http://www.ned.org/where-we-work/asia/china-tibet |title=美国国家民主基金会在西藏地区项目列表 |access-date=2012-02-06 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20141109151527/http://www.ned.org/where-we-work/asia/china-tibet |archive-date=2014-11-09 |dead-url=no }}</ref>。

